{"tid":1239192,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"老馬:屌你老母垃圾阿根廷","createTime":"2019-06-18T05:50:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T14:51:47.000Z","uid":226925,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"3f848eff34b6bd374d117adf833ff0840ab2329e","tid":1239192,"uid":226925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:50:20.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】阿根廷於美洲國家盃首輪以0:2不敵哥倫比亞，前教練兼球王馬勒當拿發火炮轟一眾球員。<br />\n<br />\n我認為湯加也可以擊敗我們。」馬勒當拿（Diego Maradona）說。「我們以雙腳踢出聲望。記得那時圍攻秘魯嗎？記得那時打破大巴嗎？現在剩下了甚麼？」<br />\n<br />\n老馬更爆粗狠批球員不值得代表阿根廷國家隊：「這件球衣是甚麼？你們完全是侮辱了這件球衣，XXXXX！」阿根廷在周三美洲國家盃B組次輪將鬥巴拉圭，若再敗出線將有危機。"},{"pid":"9d64d70b1e7a2e57bd8f80610c1a5a6f2e412a04","tid":1239192,"uid":23385,"like":31,"dislike":4,"score":27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:55:56.000Z","msg":"邊有出線危機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一隊巴拉龜一隊卡㙮爾<br />\n有牙花點會連輸兩場"},{"pid":"89c06cf5c8328cf2053861a847dcc753cd7bd450","tid":1239192,"uid":3480,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:58:40.000Z","msg":"XXXXX<br />\n中文係咩"},{"pid":"10e0e661d0e429e7992b29d171cc65bdb6689f2f","tid":1239192,"uid":218659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:09:35.000Z","msg":"又割蓆 分化撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d5cc2ac320cdf8581ebde9312bdae51298cde1","tid":1239192,"uid":99861,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"89c06cf5c8328cf2053861a847dcc753cd7bd450","tid":1239192,"uid":3480,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:58:40.000Z","msg":"XXXXX<br />\n中文係咩"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:12:11.000Z","msg":"佩雷斯主席"},{"pid":"8b48ef497b93c5290f81cc75b05482da716a9c13","tid":1239192,"uid":53855,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9d64d70b1e7a2e57bd8f80610c1a5a6f2e412a04","tid":1239192,"uid":23385,"like":31,"dislike":4,"score":27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:55:56.000Z","msg":"邊有出線危機<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma